WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: uz

00:00:00.200 --> 00:00:03.360
Umid qilamanki, ushbu kod blokini 
terish harakati sizni boshqa 

00:00:03.360 --> 00:00:07.330
bayonotlarni yozishda yanada 
qulay his qildi va sizga dastur 

00:00:07.330 --> 00:00:11.710
yaratishda qandaydir qiziqarli mantiqni joriy
qilish uchun undan qanday foydalanishingiz mumkinligini tushuntirdi.

00:00:11.710 --> 00:00:14.650
O‘zgaruvchan sonli 
mehmonlar rasmidagi 

00:00:14.650 --> 00:00:17.380
bu oxirgi savol o‘nga teng.

00:00:17.380 --> 00:00:21.860
Keyin bu birinchi shart noto‘g‘ri bo‘ladi, 
chunki o‘ntasi oltitadan kam emas.

00:00:21.860 --> 00:00:23.360
Shunday qilib, biz bu ishni 
o‘tkazib yubormoqdamiz.

00:00:23.360 --> 00:00:27.120
Ikkinchi shartga o‘tamiz 10 
kishining soni 

00:00:27.120 --> 00:00:27.800
20 dan kamligini tekshiramiz.

00:00:27.800 --> 00:00:31.670
Va bu to‘g‘ri, shuning uchun 
biz uchni 100 ga o‘rnatdik.

00:00:31.670 --> 00:00:36.620
Ushbu holatga tushib qolganimizdan 
so‘ng, biz boshqa barcha hollarni 

00:00:36.620 --> 00:00:39.469
tashlab yuborishimiz mumkin va 
keyin uchining qiymati 100 ga teng bo‘ladi.

